<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Cotton Family Weekly Plan</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --cream: #FAF7F2;
    --warm-white: #FFFDF9;
    --rust: #C4622D;
    --rust-light: #F0E0D6;
    --iron: #7B4F3A;
    --sage: #6B7F6E;
    --sage-light: #E4EDE5;
    --debra-pink: #D4607A;
    --debra-bg: #FFF0F3;
    --bryan-blue: #2C6B8A;
    --bryan-bg: #EEF5FA;
    --workout-purple: #6B4F8A;
    --workout-bg: #F3F0F8;
    --workout-border: #D4C8E8;
    --text: #2A1F1A;
    --text-mid: #6B5C54;
    --border: #E8DDD6;
    --training-bg: #FEF4EF;
    --rest-bg: #F0F4F0;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  header {
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 28px 24px 24px;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  header p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #B0A49C;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Top tabs */
  .main-tabs {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--warm-white);
  }

  .main-tab {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -2px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .main-tab.active { color: var(--text); border-bottom-color: var(--text); }
  .main-tab.active-workout { color: var(--workout-purple); border-bottom-color: var(--workout-purple); }
  .main-tab.active-tracker { color: var(--debra-pink); border-bottom-color: var(--debra-pink); }

  /* Person toggle */
  .person-tabs {
    display: flex;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .person-tab {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -1px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .person-tab.active-debra { color: var(--debra-pink); border-bottom-color: var(--debra-pink); }
  .person-tab.active-bryan { color: var(--bryan-blue); border-bottom-color: var(--bryan-blue); }
  .person-tab.active-both { color: var(--text); border-bottom-color: var(--text); }

  /* View panels */
  .view-panel { display: none; }
  .view-panel.active { display: block; }

  /* Macro bars */
  .macros-bar { display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .macro-block {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--warm-white);
  }
  .macro-block:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .macro-block .label {
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .macro-block .value {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .macro-block.debra .value { color: var(--debra-pink); }
  .macro-block.bryan .value { color: var(--bryan-blue); }

  .macro-block .sub { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-mid); }

  .iron-banner {
    background: var(--iron);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .iron-banner strong { font-weight: 600; }

  /* Day cards */
  .week-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0; }

  .day-card { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--warm-white); }

  .day-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 20px 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .day-header.training { background: var(--training-bg); }
  .day-header.rest { background: var(--rest-bg); }

  .day-name {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .day-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .badge.training { background: var(--rust); color: white; }
  .badge.rest { background: var(--sage); color: white; }
  .badge.iron { background: var(--iron); color: white; }
  .badge.home { background: var(--workout-purple); color: white; }

  .chevron { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); transition: transform 0.2s; margin-left: 4px; }

  .day-body { display: none; padding: 0 16px 20px; }
  .day-body.open { display: block; }

  /* Workout block inside meal day */
  .workout-inline {
    margin-top: 14px;
    background: var(--workout-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--workout-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }

  .workout-inline-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .workout-inline-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .workout-phases { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }

  .workout-phase { }

  .phase-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.7px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }

  .phase-items {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .phase-item { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: baseline; }
  .phase-num { color: var(--workout-purple); font-weight: 700; font-size: 10px; min-width: 14px; }
  .phase-sets { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 10px; }
  .phase-note { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-mid); font-style: italic; padding-left: 20px; }

  .finisher-note {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    font-style: italic;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--workout-border);
    padding-top: 6px;
  }

  /* Meal slots */
  .meal-slot { margin-top: 14px; }

  .slot-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    padding: 6px 0 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .persons-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .person-card {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .person-card.debra { background: var(--debra-bg); border-color: #F0C0CC; }
  .person-card.bryan { background: var(--bryan-bg); border-color: #C0D8E8; }

  body.view-debra .person-card.bryan-only { display: none; }
  body.view-debra .persons-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  body.view-bryan .person-card.debra-only { display: none; }
  body.view-bryan .persons-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

  .person-name-tag {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .person-card.debra .person-name-tag { color: var(--debra-pink); }
  .person-card.bryan .person-name-tag { color: var(--bryan-blue); }

  .meal-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 3px; line-height: 1.3; }
  .meal-flavor { font-size: 11px; color: var(--rust); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .meal-items { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; }

  .iron-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 9px; background: var(--iron); color: white;
    padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 10px; margin-left: 3px; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .c-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 9px; background: var(--sage); color: white;
    padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 10px; margin-left: 3px; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .shared-note {
    margin-top: 8px;
    background: #FFF8F0;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    padding: 6px 10px;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--iron);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  .day-tip {
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: #3D5240;
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  }

  /* Standalone workout view */
  .workout-view { padding: 16px; }

  .workout-card {
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--workout-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .workout-card-header {
    background: var(--workout-purple);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }

  .workout-day-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .workout-card-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .workout-section {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--workout-border);
  }

  .workout-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .section-head {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .exercise-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EAF8;
  }

  .exercise-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .ex-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    min-width: 18px;
  }

  .ex-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ex-sets {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--debra-pink);
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ex-note {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    font-style: italic;
    padding-left: 26px;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .warmup-items { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 2; }

  .finisher-box {
    background: #F3F0F8;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
  }

  .finisher-box strong { font-weight: 700; }

  .jess-note {
    margin: 0 16px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F3F0F8, #FFF0F3);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    border: 1px solid var(--workout-border);
  }

  .jess-note .note-head {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: var(--workout-purple);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  /* Legend */
  .legend {
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  footer {
    padding: 18px 24px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  /* Body Stats Tracker */
  .tracker-view { padding: 16px; }

  .baseline-card {
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .baseline-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    color: #B0A49C;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .baseline-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .baseline-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .baseline-stat {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }

  .baseline-stat .stat-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    color: #B0A49C;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .baseline-stat .stat-val {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--debra-pink);
  }

  .baseline-stat .stat-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #B0A49C;
  }

  .segmental-card {
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .segmental-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .segmental-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .seg-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .seg-item .seg-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .seg-item .seg-val {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .seg-item .seg-pct {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
  }

  .log-section {
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .log-header {
    background: var(--debra-pink);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .log-form {
    padding: 16px 18px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .log-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .log-field label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
  }

  .log-field input {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--text);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .log-field input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--debra-pink);
  }

  .log-field.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

  .log-btn {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: var(--debra-pink);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .log-btn:active { opacity: 0.85; }

  .entries-list { padding: 0 18px 16px; }

  .entry-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .entry-date {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .entry-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .entry-stat { text-align: center; }

  .entry-stat .e-val {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--debra-pink);
    display: block;
  }

  .entry-stat .e-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
  }

  .entry-delta {
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    padding-top: 6px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-mid);
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .delta-pos { color: var(--sage); font-weight: 600; }
  .delta-neg { color: var(--rust); font-weight: 600; }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .goals-card {
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border: 1px solid #C0D4C2;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .goals-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--sage);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .goal-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 4px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #C0D4C2;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .goal-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .goal-row span:last-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--sage); }

  footer strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="view-both">

<header>
  <h1>Cotton Family Weekly Plan</h1>
  <p>Starting 6/15/2026 · Meals + Home Workouts · Iron-optimized</p>
</header>

<!-- Main view tabs -->
<div class="main-tabs">
  <div class="main-tab active" onclick="setMainView('meals', this)">🍽 Meals</div>
  <div class="main-tab" onclick="setMainView('workouts', this)">💪 Workouts</div>
  <div class="main-tab" onclick="setMainView('tracker', this)">📊 Body Stats</div>
</div>

<!-- MEALS PANEL -->
<div class="view-panel active" id="panel-meals">

  <div class="person-tabs">
    <div class="person-tab active-both" onclick="setView('both', this)">👫 Both</div>
    <div class="person-tab" onclick="setView('debra', this)">💗 Debra</div>
    <div class="person-tab" onclick="setView('bryan', this)">💙 Bryan</div>
  </div>

  <div class="macros-bar" id="macrosBar"></div>

  <div class="iron-banner">
    🩸 <strong>Debra iron strategy:</strong> Spinach every breakfast · Bell peppers for absorption · Red meat 3x/week · Space dairy 1–2 hrs from iron meals
  </div>

  <div class="week-grid" id="weekGrid"></div>

  <div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--iron)"></div> High iron</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--sage)"></div> Vit C boost</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--workout-purple)"></div> Home workout day</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--debra-pink)"></div> Debra</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--bryan-blue)"></div> Bryan</div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <strong>Cook-once system:</strong> Same protein batch, same pot of rice or potatoes — weigh Bryan's portion first, then Debra's. Sauce separately where needed. Batch cook Sunday for Mon/Tue, Wednesday night for Thu/Fri.<br><br>
    <strong>Iron absorption:</strong> Heme iron (red meat) absorbs freely. Non-heme iron (spinach, eggs) needs vitamin C alongside. Avoid coffee/tea within 1 hr of meals. Space Greek yogurt snack at least 1 hr from iron-heavy meals.
  </footer>

</div>

<!-- WORKOUTS PANEL -->
<div class="view-panel" id="panel-workouts">
  <div class="workout-view">

    <div class="jess-note">
      <div class="note-head">💜 From Jess — Your Flexibility Plan</div>
      Don't view the home workout as the backup plan. View it as <strong>"My flexibility plan."</strong> Some weeks you hit all 4 gym sessions. Some weeks it's 2 gym + 2 home. The win is getting 4 workouts done and showing up for yourself — regardless of where.
    </div>

    <!-- MONDAY -->
    <div class="workout-card">
